		<title>Ugly Betty &#8211; 4&#215;01/02 &#8211; The Butterfly Effect</title>
		<link>http://www.serialmente.com/2009/10/19/ugly-betty-4x0102-the-butterfly-effect/</link>
		<comments>http://www.serialmente.com/2009/10/19/ugly-betty-4x0102-the-butterfly-effect/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 19 Oct 2009 15:22:25 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Fede</dc:creator>
