		<title>Ugly Betty &#8211; 3&#215;20 &#8211; Rabbit Test</title>
		<link>http://www.serialmente.com/2009/05/04/ugly-betty-3x20-rabbit-test/</link>
		<comments>http://www.serialmente.com/2009/05/04/ugly-betty-3x20-rabbit-test/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2009 07:30:39 +0000</pubDate>
